cs.SY, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.RO, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with the verification of dynamical systems, which is a topic in control theory and systems engineering. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely category. The paper also uses optimization-based search, which falls under cs.LO (Optimization and Control). The use of automata-based verification suggests cs.PL (Programming Languages) as a possible category. The paper also deals with temporal logic, which is a topic in cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
